column5: Anybody going, starts tomorrow 1-11-18, our gang will be there Saturday to research the Ontario outfitters. Always enjoy this very popular show here in Michigan. Moon
I'll probably go tomorrow -- lots to do there and always enjoy the boats.

I've been going now for 4 years. 1 1/2 hr drive from Ontario but well worth it in my eyes. always enjoy the seminars. We make a day of it and get a nice breakfast in Novi and are waiting for he doors to open at 11.
its been a few years so im due, probably Saturday
